<view class="help-page"><scroll-view class="help-scroll" scroll-y="{{true}}" show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view class="help-section"><view class="help-card"><view class="card-head"><uni-icons wx:if="{{a}}" u-i="4f651d5d-0" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{a}}"></uni-icons><text class="card-title">伴游人员邀请码</text></view><view class="invite-row" bindtap="{{c}}"><text class="invite-code">{{b}}</text><view class="invite-copy">点击复制</view></view><text class="card-tip">出示邀请码给工作人员，快速建立协助关系。</text></view><view class="help-card"><view class="card-head"><uni-icons wx:if="{{d}}" u-i="4f651d5d-1" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{d}}"></uni-icons><text class="card-title">场馆帮助热线</text></view><text class="contact-line">电话：400-000-0000</text><text class="contact-line">微信：长乔海洋公园</text><image class="contact-qr" src="{{e}}" mode="aspectFit"/><text class="card-tip">扫码可联系场馆客服获取帮助。</text></view><view class="help-card"><view class="card-head"><uni-icons wx:if="{{f}}" u-i="4f651d5d-2" bind:__l="__l" u-p="{{f}}"></uni-icons><text class="card-title">感官友好书包</text></view><button class="{{['apply-btn', h && 'done']}}" bindtap="{{i}}">{{g}}</button><view wx:if="{{j}}" class="apply-info"><text class="apply-line">申请状态：{{k}}</text><text class="apply-line">申请时间：{{l}}</text><text class="apply-line">关联邀请码：{{m}}</text></view></view></view><view class="bottom-space"></view></scroll-view></view>